### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@travelRequestId = 8
@legId = 1
@approverId = 100

### 01-Create Travel Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "costCenterCode": "IT-001",
  "costCenterName": "IT Development",
  "destination": "Berlin",
  "purpose": "Kundentermin bei ABC GmbH - Präsentation neuer Softwarelösungen",
  "startDate": "2025-12-15",
  "endDate": "2025-12-16",
  "estimatedAmount": 450.50,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### 02-Get Travel Request By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}

### 03-Get Travel Requests By Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests?employeeId=1

### 04-Submit Travel Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/submit

### 05-Get Pending Approvals
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/pending-approvals

### 06-Approve Travel Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approverId": {{approverId}}
}

### 07-Reject Travel Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approverId": {{approverId}},
  "reason": "Die geschätzten Kosten überschreiten das Budget. Bitte prüfen Sie günstigere Alternativen."
}

### 08-Add Travel Leg
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/travel-legs
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "departureLocation": "Hamburg",
    "arrivalLocation": "München",
    "transportationType": "FLIGHT",
    "costAmount": 149.99,
    "currency": "EUR",
    "description": "Lufthansa LH2022",
    "departureDateTime": "2025-12-15T09:30:00",
    "arrivalDateTime": "2025-12-15T11:15:00",
    "distanceKm": 612.0
  }
]

### 09-Get Travel Legs
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/travel-legs

### 10-Remove Travel Leg
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/travel-requests/{{travelRequestId}}/travel-legs/{{legId}}

### 11-Add Multiple Travel Legs (Complete Route)
